16 meirt
Londen Ar John Kent & comp
mij last to you was 5 curs, sencerec yours of 17 & 21 past, the ostendish
convoij is arrived, butt not that from hull, which I pray gods send well
yd opinion is that the best times comes on to buy goods, so lett mys
order from the north be compleated, which is for 150 not s0 as you
write white kersies 30 gend one pack of heavie gayes, & 2 of cloth
which clothes to be assorted to my order of 2 curt, & now desire you
to buy 3 such packes, that is one pack more then ordered, assorted, as to
the direction given 2 cart. from london buy the rest of spanish clothe
yett non to exceed iop neither anney of the newest cullours, butt to
N1„ 2„ 3, 4 a 5, 6, of the patt sent 1o Jannnary, for you have not sent
all the white or silver grayes & as yett not one gray that hath the
liveley hood of N2, att which I wonder, there fore endeavour to
gett that cullour, I say such liveley gray of anney price from 6 to dp
& 2a 3 p to N4 & 6 of 7 ƒ 8, a9 ƒ with a botwne mode or 2 of 7 ƒ
a yd which sp to be send by anney convoy that shall depart firt, as also
the pennestons, devonshire bayes, adding to that pack 8 a 10 p of white
franels from 13 „ 14 to 26 a 22 pence a yd, which white goood may come by
way of holland & the sp clothes for next convoij for ostend prepare 2 a 3
packes each pack to cont: 8 demie reds 2 red pennestons, of the broadest
4 best & 3 a 4 white cottons the cottons to be from 20 to 24 pence a
goad the best forred, butt if you iudge the cottons will come cheaper then
buy butt one pack now: you send in N5 acloth N 45, which cullour will
never do & bj no meane to anney of my patt. ordered further I know not
what to do with the 2 scarlett of last yeare non will have them because of
their spoiled cullour, so that I must returne them, pray minde my bussynes
& negleet not mij orders adviseinge what passes remaine
lett amonght the flanels 2 a 4 p gehepert, that is 16 fin

de ue aengenaeme van 27 Jan &, 14 & 17 feb laest op hunen tyde
ontfangen, antwoorde gedilayeert om dat ick tot noch toe te gemoet
sien mijn remise van 1 £100 op willem purnell, de welcke in gevalle
o ontfanck deser herrewaert niet is versonden, by ue geliest te
houden, de weirde in voorderen, & op mijne rekeninge stellen op de
welke ue is gecrediteert voor de £105:15 p soo mijn pack N8
